## Obfuscated function and variable names with food

'Subtracts the value used by the caesar cipher
Function Pears(Beets)
    Pears = Chr(Beets - 17)
End Function

'Gets rid of the first 3 chars which were decrypted
Function Strawberries(Grapes)
    Strawberries = Left(Grapes, 3)
End Function

Function Almonds(Jelly)
    Almonds = Right(Jelly, Len(Jelly) - 3)
End Function

'performs the decryption of the encrypted string
Function Nuts(Milk)
    Do
    Oatmilk = Oatmilk + Pears(Strawberries(Milk))

    Nuts = Oatmilk
End Function
